sources.description:
Monte Ashcroft, a world-class editorial photographer is struck by a new muse while traveling out to the desert for a shoot when he stops in at a desolate diner and meets Dakota. Monte extends an open invitation to help her break into modeling should she ever decide to move to LA. Their connection is instant and profound, with the exception of one big secret.

2024.  Stars: Will Hirschfeld, Ashley Moore, Jonathan Kowalsky
